name: ANIMAL_ID
title: ANIMAL_ID
description: INTERBULL REGISTRATION CODE WHICH HAS EXACTLY 19 CHARACTERS. MADE UP OF FOUR COMPONENTS: BREED (3), COUNTRY (3), SEX(1), REGISTRATION NUMBER(12)

name: GENOTYPE
title: GENOTYPE
description: USING THE CDCB FORMAT ; THE GENOTYPE IS A VARIABLE LENGTH STRING OF 0,1,2,5 INDICATING SNP GENOTYPES OF BB, AB, AA, \\-\\- (1 BYTE PER SNP, NO COMMAS BETWEEN SNPS). FOR EXAMPLE \'01252010250211110025.......\'.

name: SAMPLE_ID
title: SAMPLE_ID
description: UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES GENOTYPE (ie. SENTRIX CODE); DO NOT USE THE ANIMAL_ID (REGISTRATION NUM) TO ALLOW FOR MULTIPLE GENOTYPES PER ANIMAL IF REQUIRED

name: SOURCE_OF_DATA
title: SOURCE_OF_DATA
description: See contacts list under \'Source of Data\' column
